| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1173 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 161bf6ba-bcf1-510c-a99e-1def694f6ac3"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
